WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:56.600 --> 00:02:01.810
How can someone like you, with no 
damn pride, be a pirate captain?

3
00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:01.810
Happiness

4
00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:04.990
What in the world can you do?

5
00:02:06.710 --> 00:02:08.610
I can defeat you!

6
00:02:11.590 --> 00:02:13.900
That's right, you damn idiot!

7
00:02:13.900 --> 00:02:16.860
If he dies, I'm gonna kill him!

8
00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:19.820
I've got your back!

9
00:02:19.820 --> 00:02:22.270
That's it, Gum-Gum!

10
00:02:22.270 --> 00:02:24.520
Get him, Big Bro Luffy!

11
00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:27.080
You've got this! 
You're on the same level!

12
00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:30.460
Go to hell, worm!

13
00:02:31.250 --> 00:02:34.250
Ugh! He's got new teeth!

14
00:02:34.250 --> 00:02:38.090
I'm a shark. New teeth 
grow in one after another.

15
00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:42.220
And they're sturdier 
than the previous ones.

16
00:02:44.380 --> 00:02:46.180
Each and every time!

17
00:02:50.150 --> 00:02:52.150
Whoa!

18
00:02:52.150 --> 00:02:53.970
As many times as I want!

19
00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:05.200
The heavens have bestowed this trait to us.

20
00:03:06.580 --> 00:03:08.200
That's amazing!

21
00:03:08.730 --> 00:03:14.170
Are you starting to realize what 
a superior race the fishmen are?

22
00:03:18.090 --> 00:03:21.050
Tooth & Gum!

23
00:03:21.050 --> 00:03:21.990
Huh?

24
00:03:26.970 --> 00:03:27.850
Stop!

25
00:03:36.570 --> 00:03:38.860
Big Bro Luffy!

26
00:03:47.990 --> 00:03:50.000
A-Arlong...

27
00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:53.000
that hurt.

28
00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:55.250
Wh-Wha...! B-Brother!

29
00:03:57.570 --> 00:03:58.760
Phew.

30
00:03:59.300 --> 00:04:02.230
You rubber punk!

31
00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:07.220
How dare you use my 
brother as a shield!

32
00:04:07.220 --> 00:04:09.000
What're you talking about?

33
00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.180
You're the one who attacked.

34
00:04:11.180 --> 00:04:14.280
Phew... That sure was scary.

35
00:04:16.300 --> 00:04:18.450
Don't move,

36
00:04:18.450 --> 00:04:20.490
you rubber bastard!

37
00:04:22.050 --> 00:04:22.950
Oh yeah!

38
00:04:22.950 --> 00:04:24.700
I've got a fun idea.

39
00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:26.690
A fun idea?

40
00:04:26.690 --> 00:04:28.660
What in the world will he...?

41
00:04:28.660 --> 00:04:31.320
Does he have some 
trick up his sleeve?

42
00:04:32.620 --> 00:04:34.790
Tooth & Gum!

43
00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:02.110
There we go!

44
00:05:04.300 --> 00:05:05.630
Idiot,

45
00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:09.890
it's useless for you to keep 
destroying my teeth.

46
00:05:11.200 --> 00:05:13.620
You still don't get it?!

47
00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:16.440
B-Big Bro Luffy,

48
00:05:16.440 --> 00:05:19.130
surely you didn't mean 
that this is your fun idea.

49
00:05:19.130 --> 00:05:22.360
Look! I've got fangs, too!

50
00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:30.640
S-So he didn't have 
a trick up his sleeve?

51
00:05:34.100 --> 00:05:36.560
How long are you going to

52
00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.900
keep fooling around?!

53
00:05:41.580 --> 00:05:44.440
The shark bit me!

54
00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:47.530
That's because you're playing around!

55
00:05:47.990 --> 00:05:50.700
I'm not trying to mess around.

56
00:05:50.700 --> 00:05:52.880
Tooth & Gum!

57
00:06:15.770 --> 00:06:17.770
Arlong bit him!

58
00:06:25.290 --> 00:06:28.430
How do you like that? 
A tooth for a tooth!

59
00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:32.560
You can use my teeth all you want.

60
00:06:33.700 --> 00:06:36.290
You're still stuck with that weak jaw.

61
00:06:36.290 --> 00:06:37.810
Listen up.

62
00:06:38.310 --> 00:06:43.200
A shark's teeth are only 
as good as his jaws,

63
00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:45.660
which tear through flesh!

64
00:06:47.420 --> 00:06:50.510
Ahh! Big Bro's gonna lose his arm!

65
00:06:50.510 --> 00:06:51.800
Luffy!

66
00:07:31.100 --> 00:07:33.140
Is his arm okay?

67
00:07:34.200 --> 00:07:37.410
If he backed off even a step, 
he would've lost that arm!

68
00:07:37.410 --> 00:07:42.750
I doubt he thought too much about what the fangs'd do to him, though.

69
00:08:03.050 --> 00:08:04.090
Huh?

70
00:08:05.390 --> 00:08:07.000
Where'd he go?

71
00:08:07.590 --> 00:08:08.790
Luffy! The sea!

72
00:08:08.790 --> 00:08:09.840
The sea?

73
00:08:12.300 --> 00:08:13.760
There's a shark!

74
00:08:15.060 --> 00:08:16.970
That's Arlong!

75
00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:24.170
What? Did he dive down?

76
00:08:25.220 --> 00:08:30.140
This is serious! 
He's twice as powerful in the water.

77
00:08:33.310 --> 00:08:38.410
No one can stop me once
I gather speed underwater.

78
00:08:38.410 --> 00:08:43.660
This ability is precisely the kind
bestowed only to fishmen.

79
00:08:45.100 --> 00:08:46.670
Did he run away?

80
00:08:57.690 --> 00:09:00.640
Shark Gone...

81
00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:02.890
Darts!

82
00:09:08.770 --> 00:09:10.190
What was that?!

83
00:09:10.800 --> 00:09:12.320
A torpedo?!

84
00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:18.240
Something flew out of the sea!

85
00:09:18.870 --> 00:09:22.700
Ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow...

86
00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:31.630
Wow, you handled that well.

87
00:09:31.630 --> 00:09:36.930
But the more you dodge, 
the more hell you'll get.

88
00:09:36.930 --> 00:09:42.140
Shark Gone Darts!

89
00:09:50.310 --> 00:09:54.320
Wh-What the hell are those 
damn shark's bones made of?!

90
00:09:55.190 --> 00:09:57.280
His nose shattered the ground!

91
00:09:57.280 --> 00:10:00.740
Shark Gone Darts!

92
00:10:16.510 --> 00:10:21.020
Hey Luffy, you gotta hide! 
Arlong went into the sea again!

93
00:10:22.470 --> 00:10:25.190
Big Bro! Please hurry and hide!

94
00:10:25.190 --> 00:10:27.480
He'll target you again!

95
00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:33.400
Get out of there!

96
00:10:36.090 --> 00:10:38.510
N-No.

97
00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:43.450
Don't be stupid! Are you trying 
to be a target?! Take cover!

98
00:10:43.890 --> 00:10:48.460
I don't want to! I'll catch him 
and break his nose!

99
00:10:48.460 --> 00:10:51.690
Come at me, shark!

100
00:10:54.700 --> 00:10:56.690
You got some nerve.

101
00:10:56.690 --> 00:11:00.590
Or have you realized that running 
away is not gonna save you?

102
00:11:01.470 --> 00:11:04.980
Can't you see that you've 
gotta hide, Luffy?!

103
00:11:04.980 --> 00:11:08.990
You barely dodged his attacks,
but they all grazed you!

104
00:11:08.990 --> 00:11:13.140
That move will instantly kill 
you if you take its full force!

105
00:11:13.140 --> 00:11:15.020
Gum-Gum...

106
00:11:15.020 --> 00:11:20.070
Shield!

107
00:11:20.070 --> 00:11:21.820
What's that stance?

108
00:11:21.820 --> 00:11:24.030
He wouldn't try to stop
the attack like that, right?

109
00:11:24.690 --> 00:11:26.990
I have twice the distance 
to accelerate this time!

110
00:11:27.500 --> 00:11:30.100
I'll punch through your heart!

111
00:11:30.100 --> 00:11:34.790
Shark Gone Darts!

112
00:11:40.510 --> 00:11:42.410
It's a direct hit!

113
00:11:55.150 --> 00:11:57.280
Wait, did he get hit?!

114
00:11:57.280 --> 00:12:00.240
No! He flung himself away!

115
00:12:02.980 --> 00:12:05.980
You're done! That attack 
won't work anymore.

116
00:12:05.980 --> 00:12:09.790
Shark Gone Darts!

117
00:12:14.880 --> 00:12:17.840
You bastard! 
That was just a lucky guess!

118
00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.590
This is the final blow!

119
00:12:19.590 --> 00:12:21.550
You won't hit me!

120
00:12:21.550 --> 00:12:23.510
Gum-Gum...

121
00:12:23.510 --> 00:12:25.300
Net!

122
00:12:26.760 --> 00:12:29.430
Fishing! I'm fishing!

123
00:12:34.900 --> 00:12:36.500
And...

124
00:12:39.680 --> 00:12:41.490
Spear!

125
00:12:47.410 --> 00:12:49.620
Whoa!

126
00:12:55.210 --> 00:12:57.790
Hm? Is he dead?

127
00:12:59.710 --> 00:13:02.170
The look in Arlong's eyes changed!

128
00:13:02.170 --> 00:13:07.140
He looks just like 
the sea kings when they attack.

129
00:13:07.140 --> 00:13:09.720
Luffy's last attack must've pissed him off!

130
00:13:12.180 --> 00:13:16.150
I've never seen Arlong with a look like that.

131
00:13:16.150 --> 00:13:19.320
Inferior human!

132
00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:23.230
What do you think
you're doing to me?!

133
00:13:24.060 --> 00:13:27.000
I'm a fishman!

134
00:13:34.810 --> 00:13:36.880
Boy, was that a shocker!

135
00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:41.000
It didn't hurt,
but he's definitely pissed.

136
00:13:51.390 --> 00:13:53.140
What the heck is that?

137
00:13:53.140 --> 00:13:54.770
Kiribachi!

138
00:13:54.770 --> 00:13:57.730
That's a monster saw!

139
00:14:19.130 --> 00:14:22.090
– Big Bro Luffy! 
– Hang in there, Luffy!

140
00:14:22.090 --> 00:14:25.090
Run! Watch out!
The attack is relentless. 
He's cornered!

141
00:14:32.890 --> 00:14:34.600
He escaped into the building!

142
00:14:41.420 --> 00:14:44.820
It's the left window on the top floor.

143
00:14:46.010 --> 00:14:47.820
That room is...

144
00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:51.200
There's nowhere left to run.

145
00:14:51.800 --> 00:14:55.870
This is the top floor of Arlong Park.

146
00:14:55.870 --> 00:14:58.190
What's this room?

147
00:14:58.190 --> 00:14:59.750
It's full of papers.

148
00:14:59.750 --> 00:15:01.870
They're no ordinary papers.

149
00:15:01.870 --> 00:15:06.210
This room is where I make that 
girl draw sea charts. It's...

150
00:15:07.590 --> 00:15:09.220
...the survey room!

151
00:15:09.790 --> 00:15:11.400
Nami's room.

152
00:15:11.400 --> 00:15:15.580
These are the sea charts 
that Nami drew.

153
00:15:16.720 --> 00:15:22.690
Across the globe, few could draw charts as accurate as these!

154
00:15:23.340 --> 00:15:26.150
The girl has a gift.

155
00:15:32.410 --> 00:15:35.800
There's nothing as sad and senseless

156
00:15:35.800 --> 00:15:38.390
as letting natural-born talent go to waste.

157
00:15:38.390 --> 00:15:44.000
She'll find true happiness
in staying here and drawing charts!

158
00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:47.880
This pen is stained with blood.

159
00:15:47.880 --> 00:15:53.090
Nami's charts are absolutely vital 
if I'm to attain world supremacy!

160
00:15:55.550 --> 00:16:01.090
She's going to continue drawing 
sea charts! All for my ambition!

161
00:16:01.090 --> 00:16:04.690
Once we've learned everything about the world's seas from those charts,

162
00:16:04.690 --> 00:16:10.380
we fishmen will be invincible,
and my empire will span the globe!

163
00:16:11.530 --> 00:16:16.490
This island and the East Blue
are the springboards for that end!

164
00:16:18.950 --> 00:16:23.920
How could you possibly use 
her as effectively as that?!

165
00:16:35.290 --> 00:16:37.100
What the...?! Kiribachi...

166
00:16:37.100 --> 00:16:39.480
isn't budging!

167
00:16:45.970 --> 00:16:46.980
What?!

168
00:16:48.700 --> 00:16:50.180
"Use"?!

169
00:16:52.230 --> 00:16:54.350
What's goin' on inside?!

170
00:16:54.350 --> 00:16:58.280
Dammit! What happened, 
Big Bro Luffy?!

171
00:16:59.480 --> 00:17:02.250
I can't tell what's going 
on up there at all.

172
00:17:05.190 --> 00:17:06.540
Luffy.

173
00:17:07.210 --> 00:17:10.570
What do you take her for?!

174
00:17:12.450 --> 00:17:15.580
She's an inferior creature, 
but a smart girl.

175
00:17:15.580 --> 00:17:18.300
If you compare all other humans to sewer rats,

176
00:17:18.300 --> 00:17:21.280
then she's a sassy little cat.

177
00:17:21.280 --> 00:17:23.680
After all, she is adorable.

178
00:17:24.200 --> 00:17:29.190
I'm going to keep on feeding her 
and buying her the clothes she likes.

179
00:17:29.190 --> 00:17:32.780
She'll have everything 
she needs to live.

180
00:17:32.780 --> 00:17:38.020
All she needs to do is keep 
drawing charts for me.

181
00:17:39.410 --> 00:17:43.000
She will forever be my tool...

182
00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:46.620
no, a part of my crew.

183
00:17:54.840 --> 00:17:56.130
What's that?!

184
00:17:58.790 --> 00:18:00.260
A desk...?

185
00:18:01.710 --> 00:18:04.300
Wh-Whew, it's just a desk.

186
00:18:04.300 --> 00:18:07.980
Man, that scared me. I thought 
it was Big Bro Luffy for sure.

187
00:18:07.980 --> 00:18:09.620
Hold on, partner!

188
00:18:09.620 --> 00:18:12.940
Are you sayin' you don't have 
faith in Big Bro Luffy's strength?!

189
00:18:12.940 --> 00:18:16.600
Wha...?!
You were scared too, Johnny!

190
00:18:16.600 --> 00:18:20.090
D-Don't be stupid! 
I was, uh, you know...

191
00:18:20.090 --> 00:18:22.280
I-I naturally thought
it was that damn Arlong!

192
00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:25.390
Huh?! It sounds like you're trying to pull one over on me!

193
00:18:25.390 --> 00:18:30.450
Say what, you jerk?! Of course, 
Big Bro Luffy'd never lose!

194
00:18:30.450 --> 00:18:31.940
Luffy?

195
00:18:33.340 --> 00:18:35.300
What do you think you're doing?!

196
00:18:37.260 --> 00:18:40.890
What the hell is going on?! 
All that random crap is flying about!

197
00:18:50.060 --> 00:18:53.700
Alright! As of today, 
this is your room!

198
00:18:53.700 --> 00:18:55.890
Your desk, your pens...

199
00:18:55.890 --> 00:18:59.030
Everything you'll need is here!

200
00:19:02.990 --> 00:19:04.790
Stop that!

201
00:19:05.950 --> 00:19:07.370
The charts!

202
00:19:09.490 --> 00:19:10.710
M-My charts!

203
00:19:14.040 --> 00:19:15.280
You damn brat!

204
00:19:15.280 --> 00:19:16.960
Don't think you can trick me,

205
00:19:17.900 --> 00:19:20.680
drawin' fake charts like that!

206
00:19:22.100 --> 00:19:25.760
Do you have the time to be 
drawing crap like this in secret?

207
00:19:28.930 --> 00:19:33.800
Try to fool me again, and I'll drag people from the village one by one

208
00:19:33.800 --> 00:19:36.290
and make you watch as I wring their necks!

209
00:19:36.290 --> 00:19:38.190
They'll meet the same fate as her!

210
00:19:43.240 --> 00:19:45.980
Damn you! I spent eight years 
making her draw those!

211
00:19:45.980 --> 00:19:49.200
I invested eight years in those 
charts! In my ambition!

212
00:19:53.300 --> 00:19:55.360
Bell-mère-san...

213
00:19:56.290 --> 00:19:58.130
Nojiko...!

214
00:20:03.340 --> 00:20:06.730
This is a pretty intense fight!

215
00:20:06.730 --> 00:20:09.200
Yeah! Looks like a fight to the death!

216
00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:10.310
Definitely!

217
00:20:18.790 --> 00:20:20.530
Thank you!

218
00:20:28.090 --> 00:20:30.870
You've gone too far, 
you rubber freak!

219
00:20:32.600 --> 00:20:35.390
"Fishmen are great" and...

220
00:20:35.390 --> 00:20:38.990
"sea charts" this, 
"circumstances" that...

221
00:20:38.990 --> 00:20:41.710
I don't know much
about any of that stuff...

222
00:20:41.710 --> 00:20:46.270
but I finally figured out how to save her!

223
00:20:51.910 --> 00:20:54.900
This room is why she 
can't leave this place!

224
00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:59.900
She doesn't want to be here, 
so I'll just destroy it all!

225
00:21:00.610 --> 00:21:02.820
Gum-Gum...

226
00:21:04.400 --> 00:21:06.140
Don't get cocky!

227
00:21:06.140 --> 00:21:10.660
Scum like you could never 
bring down Arlong Park!

228
00:21:11.330 --> 00:21:13.250
Shark Gone Cog!

229
00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:18.000
Battle Axe!

230
00:22:01.170 --> 00:22:04.380
L-Look at what that impact 
has done to Arlong Park!

231
00:22:05.590 --> 00:22:07.210
Impossible! It's gonna collapse!

232
00:22:07.210 --> 00:22:09.050
This is dangerous! 
Everyone, get back!

233
00:22:10.300 --> 00:22:11.760
Big Sis Nami! Hurry!

234
00:22:11.760 --> 00:22:13.030
But Luffy's still inside!

235
00:22:13.030 --> 00:22:13.770
Big Sis!

236
00:22:13.770 --> 00:22:15.310
Luffy! What about Luffy?!

237
00:22:20.810 --> 00:22:22.780
Luffy!

238
00:22:35.630 --> 00:22:37.000
Luffy.

239
00:22:46.840 --> 00:22:48.100
Luffy.

240
00:23:00.600 --> 00:23:05.100
Oww!

241
00:23:05.100 --> 00:23:08.000
What's all this damn noise?

242
00:23:12.810 --> 00:23:14.130
Luffy.

243
00:23:27.170 --> 00:23:30.990
Arlong Park... collapsed!

244
00:23:30.990 --> 00:23:32.880
Big Bro.

245
00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:36.140
What the hell happened inside?

246
00:23:36.900 --> 00:23:38.590
Who won?!

247
00:23:38.590 --> 00:23:42.100
Given all this debris, 
don't tell me it was...

248
00:23:43.200 --> 00:23:44.840
Luffy...

249
00:23:55.370 --> 00:23:56.470
Luffy!

250
00:23:56.470 --> 00:24:00.330
Big Bro!

251
00:24:04.190 --> 00:24:07.090
Is he okay?!

252
00:24:13.050 --> 00:24:14.830
Nami!

253
00:24:19.020 --> 00:24:22.230
You're one of us!

254
00:24:33.870 --> 00:24:35.280
I know!
